Hith, 69 Miles. and at 69 M. enter Hith alias Hide or East-Hith, formerly containing 4 Parishes, but by the choking up it's Haven and other Accidents reduc'd to one; is one of the Cinque-ports: Govern'd by a Mayor, 5 Jurats and 12 Common-Councel Men; hath 2 well endow'd Hospitals; a well furnish'd Market on Saturdays, and 2 Fairs annu∣ally, on St. Peter's Day, and the 20th. of November.

